パッケージ org.bukkit.block

Classes used to manipulate the voxels in a world, including special states.

参照先: 説明

    インタフェース 説明
    Banner  
    Beacon
    Represents a beacon.
    Block
    Represents a block.
    BlockState
    Represents a captured state of a block, which will not change automatically.
    BrewingStand
    Represents a brewing stand.
    Chest
    Represents a chest.
    CommandBlock  
    CreatureSpawner
    Represents a creature spawner.
    Dispenser
    Represents a dispenser.
    Dropper
    Represents a dropper.
    EndGateway
    Represents an end gateway.
    Furnace
    Represents a furnace.
    Hopper
    Represents a hopper.
    Jukebox
    Represents a Jukebox
    NoteBlock
    Represents a note.
    Sign
    Represents either a SignPost or a WallSign
    Skull
    Represents a Skull
    Structure

    DoubleChest
